               <p>Before Mr. Common Serjeant.</p>
               <p>645. 
               <persName id="t18300218-147-defend994" type="defendantName">
                  BENJAMIN 
                  NICHOLLS
               <interp inst="t18300218-147-defend994" type="surname" value="NICHOLLS"></interp>
